name: PDFInfo
description: Information about the PDF file structure. See https://developers.virustotal.com/reference/pdf_info

children.name: acroform
children.description: Number of /AcroForm tags found in the PDF.

children.name: autoaction
children.description: Number of /AA tags found in the PDF.

children.name: embedded_file
children.description: Number of /EmbeddedFile tags found in the PDF.

children.name: encrypted
children.description: Whether the document is encrypted or not. This is defined by the /Encrypt tag.

children.name: endobj_count
children.description: Number of object definitions (endobj keyword).

children.name: endstream_count
children.description: Number of defined stream objects (stream keyword).

children.name: flash
children.description: Number of /RichMedia tags found in the PDF.

children.name: header
children.description: PDF version.

children.name: javascript
children.description: Number of /JavaScript tags found in the PDF file. Should be the same as the js field in normal scenarios.

children.name: jbig2_compression
children.description: Number of /JBIG2Decode tags found in the PDF.

children.name: js
children.description: Number of /JS tags found in the PDF file. Should be the same as javascript field in normal scenarios.

children.name: launch_action_count
children.description: Number of /Launch tags found in the PDF file.

children.name: obj_count
children.description: Number of objects definitions (obj keyword).

children.name: object_stream_count
children.description: Number of object streams.

children.name: openaction
children.description: Number of /OpenAction tags found in the PDF.

children.name: page_count
children.description: Number of pages in the PDF.

children.name: startxref
children.description: Number of startxref keywords in the PDF.

children.name: stream_count
children.description: Number of defined stream objects (stream keyword).

children.name: suspicious_colors
children.description: Number of colors expressed with more than 3 bytes (CVE-2009-3459).

children.name: trailer
children.description: Number of trailer keywords in the PDF.

children.name: xfa
children.description: Number of /XFA tags found in the PDF.

children.name: xref
children.description: Number of xref keywords in the PDF.
